lass="line">                   <span class="built_in">type</span>: <span class="string">"get"</span>,</div><div class="line">                   url: <span class="string">"ajaxUrl"</span>,</div><div class="line">                   dataType: <span class="string">"json"</span>,</div><div class="line">                   success: <span class="keyword">function</span> (data) &#123;</div><div class="line">                       <span class="keyword">if</span> (data.msg == <span class="string">"success"</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">                           switch (data.status) &#123;</div><div class="line">                               <span class="keyword">case</span> 0 :</div><div class="line">                                   this.dialog.getNone;</div><div class="line">                                   <span class="built_in">break</span>;</div><div class="line">                               <span class="keyword">case</span> 1 :</div><div class="line">                                   this.dialog.noChance;</div><div class="line">                                   <span class="built_in">break</span>;</div><div class="line">                               <span class="keyword">case</span> 2 :</div><div class="line">                                   this.dialog.getVoucher;</div><div class="line">                                   <span class="built_in">break</span>;</div><div class="line">                               <span class="keyword">case</span> 3 :</div><div class="line">                                   this.dialog.getGoods;</div><div class="line">                                   <span class="built_in">break</span>;</div><div class="line">                           &#125;</div><div class="line">                       &#125;</div><div class="line">                   &#125;);</div><div class="line">           &#125;)</div><div class="line">       &#125;</div><div class="line">   &#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在这个例子中，我创建了一个lottery对象，lottery.bindEvent()方法被分配到一个id为lottery-btn的DOM结构上。按下按钮时，调用该函数，转盘转动，发送ajax请求，根据返回的值做不同的处理。</p>
]]></content>
    
